title: How To Beat The EVIL ANIMATRONICS In "Willy's Wonderland"
author: Cinema Summary
description:
You're locked inside a restaurant full of evil animatronics who won't stop hunting you down, until they've gotten you. When you're up against eight unstoppable evil robots, what do you do?

Think you can beat Five Nights At Freddy's? Well this aint no FNAF. Thank you for watching Willy's Wonderland explained and review of how to beat.
